sql:
SELECT property_name, property_type
FROM configurations
WHERE config_id = 1;

SELECT file_path
FROM config_files
WHERE file_id = 0;

SELECT COUNT(file_id) 
FROM config_files 
WHERE upload_date = '2023-05-01';

SELECT DISTINCT access_date
FROM access_logs
ORDER BY access_date ASC;

external_knowledge:
Project configurations refer to the setup and arrangement of various components within a project; 
User access history signifies the record of user interactions with project configurations, including views and edits;
Associated file sizes refer to the total size of configuration files, architecture files, and entity files combined.

sql:
SELECT file_path, file_size
FROM config_files
WHERE file_type = 'JSON';

SELECT config_id, user_id
FROM config_changes
WHERE change_id = 0;

SELECT DISTINCT property_name
FROM configurations
ORDER BY property_name;

SELECT COUNT(file_id)
FROM config_files
WHERE config_id = 0;
